{"tid":803450,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[準備審判系列] 匯璽II全數117伙獲認購　劉生入市有父母資助","createTime":"2018-09-02T09:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T10:08:02.000Z","uid":4361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd0036570b6cceeb90cc66505cdc3f273a91448","tid":803450,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:34:31.000Z","msg":"新鴻基地產(00016)副董事總經理雷霆表示，旗下西南九龍匯璽II今日(2日)發售117伙，已全數獲認購，料可全部沽清。項目短短8日累售近500伙，套現逾70億元。<br />\n<br />\n新地代理總經理陳漢麟指出，項目只餘下111伙尚未開價，最快今日傍晚至晚上盡推，下星期會再作新一輪銷售。<br />\n<br />\n另外，旗下元朗PARK YOHO Napoli(2B期)剛獲批預售樓花同意書及入伙紙，正籌備示範單位。"},{"pid":"52b2188a0ee3bf1476edf403e3bd2a74d4ab9fad","tid":803450,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓爆呢？"},{"pid":"c83b3ca13e0504371270f770d1492ab24474a56b","tid":803450,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52b2188a0ee3bf1476edf403e3bd2a74d4ab9fad","tid":803450,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓爆呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T10:08:02.000Z","msg":"差唔多啦，咁心急"}]}